full_text: OMB APPROVAL NO. 1405-0015 EXPRESS 08-31-92 ESTIMATED BURDEN : 1 HOUR APPLICATION FOR IMMIGRANT VISA AND ALIEN REGISTRATION PART I - BIOGRAPHIC DATA INSTRUCTIONS: Complete one copy of this form for yourself and each member of your family, regardless of age, who will immigrate with you. Please print or type your answer to all questions. Questions that are Not Applicable should be so marked. If there is insufficient room on the form, answer on a separate sheet using the same numbers as appear on the form. Attach the sheet to this form. WARNING: Any false statement or concealment of a material fact may result in your permanent explusion from the United States. This form is Part I of two parts which, together with Optional Form OF-230 PART II, constitute the complete Application for Immigrant Visa and Alien Registration. 1. FAMILY NAME FIRST NAME MIDDLE NAME MISTRY MANCHHABEN CHHABILDAS 2. OTHER NAMES USED OR BY WHICH KNOWN (If married woman, give maiden name) MANCHHABEN 3. FULL NAME IN NATIVE ALPHABET (If Roman letters not used) 172257 HELIGN ESIGNEIN 4. DATE OF BIRTH 5. AGE 6. PLACE OF BIRTH (Day) (Month) (Year) (City or town) (Province) (Country) 28 JULY 1905 87 UNDACH GUJARAT INDIA NATIONALITY (If dual national, 8. SEX 9. MARITAL STATUS give both) Male Single (Never married) Married S Widowed Divorced Separated INDIAN Female Including my present marriage, I have been married ONE times. 10. PERSONAL DESCRIPTION 11.
